---
title: Pan-Fried Gnocchi with Creamy Cremini Mushrooms and Broccoli
description: Gnocchi are usually boiled in water but in this recipe we pan fry them until they're golden brown, which adds flavour. The onions, mushrooms and garlic add extra flavour to the creamy sauce. This dish is a guaranteed crowd pleaser.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pan-fried-gnocchi-e3d6f18f.jpg
